      • countKey

        public static int countKey(java.lang.Object[] s,
           java.lang.Object key)
        Counts the number of matches to the key object within an array of objects. It iterates over the array of objects and increases the key count if the iterated object matches the key object.
        Parameters:
        list - The strings to be searched.
        key - The String to be searched for.
        Returns:
        The number of successful matches of key within strings.
